Package de.isas.lipidomics.domain

Class LipidAdduct

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.isas.lipidomics.domain.LipidAdduct
  • public class LipidAdduct
extends Object
    Base class for lipid names parsed using the different grammars. This can contain a lipid, an adduct, a sum formula and a fragment.
    Author:
    nils.hoffmann
    See Also:
    LipidSpecies, Adduct, Fragment
